(1279, 177, 'sub-page-title', '<h1>About Cox Media Group</h1>'),
(1280, 177, '_sub-page-title', 'field_541302b4bd4da'),
(1281, 177, 'sub-page-content', 'Cox Media Group is an integrated broadcasting, publishing, direct marketing and digital media company that includes the national advertising rep firms of CoxReps. Additionally, CMG owns Cox Target Media, which operates Valpak, one of North Americas leading direct marketing companies, and Savings.com, a leading online source for savings. The companys operations currently include 14 broadcast television stations and one local cable channel, 57 radio stations, eight daily newspapers and more than a dozen non-daily publications, and more than 100 digital services. CMG currently operates in more than 20 media markets and reaches approximately 52 million Americans weekly, including more than 30 million TV viewers, more than 3.5 million print and online newspaper readers, and more than 14 million radio listeners. For more information about Cox Media Group, please check us out online at www.coxmediagroup.com.'),
