(238, 34, 'header', '<p style="text-align: center;">The Gamut Difference.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Gamut pairs programmatic technology with credible hands-on service. We take a pragmatica approach to delivering cross-platform television, Internet, and mobile campaign that capitalize on both data-driven insights and the foresight afforded by a heritage of media excellence. Whether locally, regionally, or nationally, Gamut executes at the right reach and the perfect frequency.</p>'),
