(704, 104, '_heading', 'field_540754668f39a'),
(705, 104, 'text_area', 'Programmatic and RTB are fast becoming industry standards. Everyone knows that liquidity and speed drive the best execution, but how do you maximize output?\r\n\r\nGamut''s Programmatic team differentiates itself in the extras: private exchanges, "try-before-you-buy" testing, and yield optimization. Our technology optimizes across the inventory value spectrum -- across display, video, and mobile -- so each party can be confident that their dollars are producing maximum value.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[layerslider id="1"]'),
