(1242, 174, '_careers-title', 'field_54107dfd249d8'),
(1243, 174, 'careers-content', 'Gamut is comprised of four channels that effectively offer a full-spectrum of smart media solutions. So, whether our customers are buying or selling inventory, they can feel certain that their dollars are producing maximum value programmatically, directly, or through a network.'),
